experiment AuPline
instrument ESR
start 2011 02 11 2000
end 2011 02 11 2400
status R
description High spectral resolution measurements of plasma lines during geomagnetically active periods with ESR and Sondrestrom radar
contact Asti Bhatt
email abhatt@haystack.mit.edu
operator Anja Stromme
submitter Anja Stromme
resources PP(16)
notes
We hope to get spectra using uncoded long pulse (320 – 480 us) and alternating
code in interleaved mode, measuring ion line at center frequency, and up and
down shifted plasma lines offset between 3-9 MHz, depending on the E-region
electron density.

